headline: SAY HELLO TO NEW MARGARITA FLAVORED ALCOHOL BEVERAGES FROM TOPO CHICO HARD
summary: This spring, Topo Chico Hard Seltzer is expanding its portfolio with new innovations in the world of flavored alcohol beverages (FAB) with Topo Chico Hard. The exciting new lineup will include margarita-inspired FABs for 21+ fans, including all-new Topo Chico Hard Margarita FAB variety pack and Topo Chico Hard Margarita MAX FAB with 8% ABV and a bolder flavor.
